      "steps": [
        "<b>Rotation:</b> The Earth rotates 360° in 24 hours.",
        "<b>The Formula:</b> 360° ÷ 24 = <b>15°</b>.",
        "<b>Rule 1:</b> Every <b>15°</b> of Longitude represents <b>1 Hour</b> of time difference.",
        "<b>Rule 2:</b> East is <b>ADD (+)</b>. West is <b>SUBTRACT (-)</b>."
      ]
