      "steps": [
        "<b>Step 1 (Difference):</b> The distance from 0° to 45°W is <b>45°</b>.",
        "<b>Step 2 (Convert):</b> 45 ÷ 15 = <b>3 Hours</b>.",
        "<b>Step 3 (Decide):</b> West is BEHIND. We <b>SUBTRACT</b> time.",
        "<b>Step 4 (Final):</b> 12:00 PM - 3 hours = <b>9:00 AM</b>."
      ]
