        "<b>Step 2:</b> 60 ÷ 15 = <b>4 Hours</b>.",
        "<b>Step 3:</b> Dhaka is further East than Cairo, so it is ahead. <b>ADD</b>.",
        "<b>Final:</b> 7:00 AM + 4 hours = <b>11:00 AM</b>."
      ]
    },
