        "<b>Step 2 (Convert):</b> Multiply hours by 15°. <br/>3 × 15 = <b>45°</b>.",
        "<b>Step 3 (Direction):</b> The time is ahead (PM vs AM), so it must be <b>East</b>.",
        "<b>Answer:</b> City X is at <b>45° East</b>."
      ]
    }
